comments: Guy can be sarcastic, but he know the English language. The way he teaches you to structure a paper is the way it needs to be done. I\'ve used his methods while I finished my Associates then later on when I got my bachelors degree. My papers were never a point of weakness even in 300 and 400 level courses.
Nice, jokes alot. Whole class consists of like 9 five-paragraph papers and some grammar.
